Text.val: 01.10.2014 GB SCR19187 Changed range of selection ACCC
-- Select MT9 clients for other bookings than payments on cashreport

SQL_STMT_U.val: select COUT_ADMNO, COUT_CLNTNO from :1/COUT where COUT202_REPORTTYPE = 'MT9' and exists(select * from :1/ACCC where ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = COUT_ADMNO and ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO = COUT_CLNTNO and ACCC_ACCT_DATE between ':2' and ':3' and (ACCC_MUTAINVESTMENT <> 0 or ACCC_MUTTYPE = 11)) and not(exists(select * from :1/TX52 where TX52_ADMNO = COUT_ADMNO and TX52_CLNTNO = COUT_CLNTNO and TX52_DATCASHREPORT between ':2' and ':3' and TX52_RPRT_TYPE = 'MT9')) group by COUT_ADMNO, COUT_CLNTNO order by COUT_ADMNO, COUT_CLNTNO for fetch only
